IVI Publishing expands licensing pact . IVI Publishing Inc said Tuesday it expanded its 1993 licensing agreement with United States Pharmacopeia ( USP ) to offer the not - for - profit organization ' s drug and pharmacological data on the Internet . The drug databases will be produced in conjunction with the Mayo Clinic and available on the clinic ' s site on the World Wide Web , IVI Publishing said . The information from USP was used earlier in commercial CD - ROMS produced jointly by IVI and the Mayo Clinic , the company said . Financial terms were not announced . IVI Publishing produces interactive multimedia health and medical information products . Its shares were unchanged Tuesday afternoon at 3 - 1 / 8 . ( ( Chicago newsdesk ( 312 ) 408 - 8787 ) ) 
